<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
<title>HPC@SICHPC</title>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>

<!--// Apply bootstrap style //-->
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
<link rel="canonical" href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/examples/sticky-footer-navbar/">
<link href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/examples/sticky-footer-navbar/sticky-footer-navbar.css" rel="stylesheet"/>

<style>
.bg-khu-red    { background-color: rgb(164,  15,  22); }
.bg-khu-blue   { background-color: rgb( 13,  50, 111); }
.bg-khu-gold   { background-color: rgb(192, 163,  83); }
.bg-khu-gray   { background-color: rgb(113, 113, 113); }
.bg-khu-silver { background-color: rgb(181, 181, 181); }

</style>

</head>

<body>
<!--// Javascript for the bootstraap //-->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.8/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-I7E8VVD/ismYTF4hNIPjVp/Zjvgyol6VFvRkX/vR+Vc4jQkC+hVqc2pM8ODewa9r" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-BBtl+eGJRgqQAUMxJ7pMwbEyER4l1g+O15P+16Ep7Q9Q+zqX6gSbd85u4mG4QzX+" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<!--// Header //-->
<header>
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark fixed-top bg-khu-red">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">SICHPC</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
</header>

<main class="flex-shrink-0">
  <div class="container">

    <div id="PAGE_HEAD">
      <h1 class="mt-2">HPC@SIC KHU</h1>
      <p class="lead">경희대학교 과학지능융합전공 HPC 서버</p>

      <p class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">
        메인 페이지 작성중입니다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div id="PAGE_BODY">

      <div id="SECTION_1">
        <h2>1. SICHPC 서버 정보</h2>
        <p class="ms-2">
          준비중
        </p>
      </div>
   
      <div id="SECTION_2">
        <h2>2. 사용방법</h2>

        <div id="SECTION_2.1">
          <h3 class="ms-2">2.1. 서버 접속하기</h3>
          <code><p class="text-light bg-dark ps-3 py-3 ms-4">
            [LOCAL_ID@localhost ~]$ ssh sichpc.khu.ac.kr -p 222 -l &lt;USER_ID&gt;<br>
            [USER_ID@sichpc ~]$
          </p></code>
          <p class="ms-4">
            학생의 경우 <code>&lt;USER_ID&gt;=s&lt;학번&gt;</code>의 형태(ex: s2023123456)로 부여되며,  수업이 진행되는 학기에만 부여됩니다.<br>
            교직원 및 대학원생의 경우 부여된 <code>&lt;USER_ID&gt;</code>를 이용하시면 됩니다. 
          </p>
        </div>
      
        <div id="SECTION_2.2">
          <h3 class="ms-2">2.2. Slurm 사용하기</h3>

          <div id="SECTION_2.2.1">
            <h3 class="ms-4">2.2.1. Options </h3>
            <p class="ms-5">
              Slurm에 Job을 제출하기 위해 사용되는 옵션들입니다. 자세한 사항은 <a href="https://slurm.schedmd.com/documentation.html">공식 메뉴얼</a>을 참조 바랍니다.
            </p>  
          </div>

          <div id="SECTION_2.2.2">
            <h3 class="ms-4">2.2.2. srun </h3>
            <p class="ms-5">
              명령어를 커맨드 라인으로 입력하여 제출하는 방식입니다.
            </p>  
            <code><p class="text-light bg-dark ps-3 py-3 ms-5">
              [USER_ID@sichpc ~]$ srun -p &lt;PartitionName&gt; hostname<br>
              gpu02<br>
              [USER_ID@sichpc ~]$ 
            </p></code>
          </div>

          <div id="SECTION_2.2.3">
            <h3 class="ms-4">2.2.3. sbatch </h3>
            <p class="ms-5">
              명령어를 스크립트로 작성하여 제출하는 방식입니다.
            </p>  
            <code><p class="text-light bg-dark ps-3 py-3 ms-5">
              [USER_ID@sichpc ~]$ sbatch &lt;script.sh&gt;<br>
              gpu02<br>
              [USER_ID@sichpc ~]$ 
            </p></code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  <\div>
</main>

<footer class="footer mt-auto py-3 bg-khu-red">
  <div class="container">
  </div>
</footer>

</body>

</html> 
